      ],
      "settings": {
        "title": "The Steps Before Honey Hunting",
        "description": "<p>Honey hunting isn’t just a solo adventure; it involves important pre-steps that happen before the actual hunt. While these preparations might not get much attention, they are what contribute to making the honey hunt victorious.</p>",
